# install
$ pip3 install --user meson
brew install meson ## ?

# troubleshooting  -- meson: No such file or directory Description: The default
installation prefix for the python pip module installation is not included in
your shell environment PATH. The default prefix for python pip installation
modules is located under /usr/local.

**Resolution: This issue can be resolved by altering the default shell environment PATH to include /usr/local/bin. **

# troubleshooting -- bad or missing python
look for stragglers installs with *._pth files esp. easy_install in site-packages

#compiling
 cd /path/to/source/root
$ meson setup builddir && cd builddir
$ meson compile
$ meson test
